{
  "schemaVersion": 3,
  "order": 361,
  "id": "elmina",
  "name": "Elmina",
  "title": "Sunkissed Mirage",
  "description": "People stare at Elmina no matter where she goes.\n\nIn human kingdoms, they stare because she's an elf. In the fair-skinned north, her tan draws curious attention. And when she's on the beach...well. She could do without the open-mouthed stares, but she likes bikinis best, so that's what she'll wear.\n\nTo tell the truth, being noticed takes some getting used to for a former street kid. That's why she learned to be stealthy. Keeping invisible saved her hide too many times to count, but it's no way to live. Not anymore.\n\nShe can slip into shadow whenever she wants. Why not enjoy a day in the sun?",
